arStrings.szText: "It seems the dregs were being hunted."
Nangari hunting dregs. But not a body eaten. This was done for territory...or for sport.
Either way, these are not the nangari of the northern swamps. They have been wounded by the dregs, and yet they show no sign of infection. Natural resistance!
thoughtful, then with excitement, newfound hope
This may well be the cure we’re looking for! Collect their blood, bring it to me.
And find out where they came from. I suspect the ruins in the south would be a good place to start. There’s no time to lose.
